name: Veak
tagline: app components for vue and electron
body:
### Welcome to veak



### npm
```
npm install veak
```

### Demo

[demo](./demo)

### Components
``` js
let components = {
	Btn,
	CheckBox,
	Dropdown,
	DropMenu,
	DropSelect,
	Flayout,
	FlexWindow,
	GridCol,
	GridRow,
	Icon,
	MenuIter,
	NavGroup,
	PureInput,
	PureSelect,
	RadioGroup,
	SimpleTab,
	SimpleTable,
	FormControl,
}
```
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
